      "date": "2012-09-12 03:35:55.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.8/x86_64, CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/fb2bd5be-fc87-11e1-bde2-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
